description: Date of matriculation from the world's premier software engineering immersive — Hack Reactor! Here I received my first true exposure to what the world of software engineering is really about. Divided into two distinct parts, the HR program begins with a grueling six-week onslaught of video and instructor-led lectures, gating student assessments and topical paired code sprints.

The 'juniors', as students of the first half of the program are known, then transition into the thesis portion of the program. The intent behind this phase is to develop a Full-Stack application that, ultimately, may serve as a testament to the student's evolution as a developer, résumé padding and content for discussion in interviews.
name: Graduated From Hack Reactor
